            }
        ]
    },
    {
        "url": "/quotes/kathy_giusti_739402",
        "quote": "Although not yet routine, many cancer centers have the technology to sequence some or all of a patient's cancer genome. This can provide massive amounts of valuable information about your cancer, including whether you have genetic mutations and other abnormalities for which new drugs are available.",
        "author": {
            "name": "Kathy Giusti",
            "url": "/quotes/kathy_giusti_739402"
        },
        "topics": [
            {
                "name": "About",
