            }
        ]
    },
    {
        "url": "/quotes/kathy_giusti_739390",
        "quote": "I'm happy to say that I am in remission. That R word is something critically important to cancer patients, especially in a disease like myeloma. But I never lose sight of the fact that there is another R word called relapse.",
        "author": {
            "name": "Kathy Giusti",
            "url": "/quotes/kathy_giusti_739390"
        },
        "topics": [
            {
                "name": "Happy",
                "url": "/topics/happy"
            },
            {
                "name": "Fact",
                "url": "/topics/fact"
            },
            {
                "name": "Another",
                "url": "/topics/another"
            }
        ]
    },
    {
        "url": "/quotes/kathy_giusti_739391",
        "quote": "In 15 years, we've raised $225 million, sequenced the myeloma genome, and opened 45 trials of 23 drugs - six approved by the FDA - which have doubled the life span of multiple myeloma patients. I've taken both Velcade and Revlimid, which we helped develop.",
        "author": {
            "name": "Kathy Giusti",
            "url": "/quotes/kathy_giusti_739391"
        },
        "topics": [
            {
                "name": "Life",
                "url": "/topics/life"
            },
            {
                "name": "Years",
                "url": "/topics/years"
            },
            {
                "name": "Approved",
                "url": "/topics/approved"
            }
        ]
    },
    {
        "url": "/quotes/kathy_giusti_739394",
        "quote": "Every time I go back to the Dana-Farber Cancer Institute to wait for my test results, and I wonder if I've relapsed or if I'm doing okay, I don't think about my company. I'm proud of everything we've done, but at the end of the day, it comes back to family. I'm still a wife, a mom, a sister - all of those things.",
        "author": {
            "name": "Kathy Giusti",
            "url": "/quotes/kathy_giusti_739394"
        },
        "topics": [
            {
                "name": "Doing",
                "url": "/topics/doing"
            },
            {
                "name": "Wait",
                "url": "/topics/wait"
            },
            {
                "name": "About",
                "url": "/topics/about"
            }
        ]
    },
    {
        "url": "/quotes/kathy_giusti_739395",
        "quote": "If I've learned anything, it's to live in the moment, and the gift that cancer gives you is, you just assume I'm only here today, and I am going to seize that moment and cherish it.",
        "author": {
            "name": "Kathy Giusti",
            "url": "/quotes/kathy_giusti_739395"
        },
        "topics": [
            {
                "name": "Gift",
