    },
    {
        "url": "/quotes/kathy_giusti_739399",
        "quote": "Despite the fact that one in every two men and one in every three women will be diagnosed with cancer in their lifetime, no one ever expects it to happen to them. I surely didn't. I was an otherwise healthy 37-year-old when I was diagnosed in 1996 with multiple myeloma, the same rare cancer Tom Brokaw has.",
        "author": {
            "name": "Kathy Giusti",
            "url": "/quotes/kathy_giusti_739399"
        },
        "topics": [
            {
                "name": "Fact",
                "url": "/topics/fact"
