                "url": "/topics/surely"
            }
        ]
    },
    {
        "url": "/quotes/kathy_giusti_739401",
        "quote": "Being treated by a doctor who specializes in your kind of cancer is so important, especially for those of us who have rare or very rare cancers. They will have access to newer treatment options that may be offered only at big academic cancer centers, so you don't miss out on treatments that could help you.",
        "author": {
            "name": "Kathy Giusti",
            "url": "/quotes/kathy_giusti_739401"
